million and $11.7 million, respectively. For the three and nine months ended September 30, 2024, the Company recognized credit loss
expense of $0.9 million and $3.0 million, respectively, which was recorded as a component of general and administrative expense in the
condensed consolidated statements of operations. For the three and nine months ended September 30, 2023, the Company recognized
credit loss expense of $0.9 million and $2.7 million, respectively, which was recorded as a component of general and administrative
expense in the condensed consolidated statements of operations.
