decrease was primarily driven by a decrease in the number of homes on our platform, lower guest demand, and, we believe, increased
supply in the market.
For the nine months ended September 30, 2024, GBV decreased by 19%, to $1,602.2 million, compared to the same period in 2023.
The decrease was primarily driven by a decrease in the number of homes on our platform, lower guest demand, and, we believe,
