raise the financing on terms acceptable to us or at all. If we are unable to raise additional capital when desired, our business, financial
condition, and results of operations could be adversely affected.
As of September 30, 2024, we had cash and cash equivalents of $124.4 million. We experienced more variable and generally weaker
