requirements, capital expenditures, and debt service obligations for at least the next 12 months.
Our future capital requirements will depend on many factors, including, but not limited to, our growth, our ability to attract and retain new
homeowners and guests that utilize our services, guest demand and booking patterns, booking channel mix, the impact of the
